{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"49076-hulum-yedimetua-tifat-new","title":"ሁሉም የድመቷ ጥፋት ነው!","description":"በታሪኩ ላይ ያለው ልጅ የቤት ስራውን መጨረስ ያቅተዋል በአንድ አስቸጋሪ ድመት ምክንያት፡፡ ተራ ምክንያት ይመስላላ? እንግዲህ ምን እንደገጠመው አንብቡ እና እንዴት አንዱ አንዱ እየመራው ሌላውም እንደዛው","language":"Amharic","langCode":"am","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Kaleab Getachew"],"illustrators":["Priya Kuriyan"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/49076-hulum-yedimetua-tifat-new"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/696669/size3/8717a72070ac52bd090aeebc8e6b36e6.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/696669/size6/8717a72070ac52bd090aeebc8e6b36e6.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13955/size6/74b224ec7927eb345bdc2c97d734e290.jpg","text":"ለምንድን ነው የቤት ስራ ያልሰራኧው？\nሚስ ይሄ እኮ የድመቷ ጥፋት ነው：：","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13956/size6/cd8835c2cbb54badb351efe4519e3c73.jpg","text":"ድመቷ ዛፍ ውስጥ ባትገባ ኖሮ እኮ እኔም መሰላሉን ለመውጣት አላመታወጣውም ነበር","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13957/size6/82dcc28b0ebb8f0b4d44834aefe31da9.jpg","text":"መሰላሉንም ለመውጣት ባላወጣው ኖሮ መጠገን አይጠበቅብኝም ነበር\nባልጠግነው ኖሮ ደግሞ ልጁም አይነሳብኝም ነበር","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13958/size6/cbebcafd09ccafb93a53ccbf97d5212d.jpg","text":"ልጁ ባይነሳ ኖሮ እናቴም ከኩሽና እየሮጠች አትመጣም ነበር\nእናቴ ሮጣ ባትመጣ ኖሮ ጦጣዋም አትገባም ነበር","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13959/size6/6afe4b32d72fda92b47269657fdd7f5e.jpg","text":"ጦጣዋ ባትገባ ኖሮ ምግቡን ሁሉ አትበላም ነበር\nሁሉንም ባትበላው ኖሮ አባቴ ሮቲስ እና ቺክን ከሪ ከ ቲ ገበያ አይገዛም ነበር","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13960/size6/47a620ff87a41f00183aa5c5d6ef823d.jpg","text":"አባቴ ሮቲስ እና ቺክን ከሪ ከ ቲ ገበያ ባይገዛ ኖሮ ውሻው አይከተለውም ነበር","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13961/size6/46fe6dae5591c1691562f296e5ec8e86.jpg","text":"ውሻው ተከትሎት ባይመጣ ኖሮ የቤትስራዬን አይበላብኝም ነበር","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13962/size6/5859bccb9c8b5fd5f6d2056c1ebeb45c.jpg","text":"ስለዚህ የምትለኝ ውሻው ያንተን የቤት ስራ በላብክ？","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13965/size6/50392cc21b95981389adaae52caf3f30.jpg","text":"አዎን ሚስ የሄ ሁሉ የድመቷ ጥፋት ነው！","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":9,"words":104}}